edu.harvard.integer.common

Class GWTWhitelist

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.integer.common.GWTWhitelist
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class GWTWhitelist
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Fake class used to force GWT to add classes to the whitelist. The white list is used to say what classes can be serialized and sent to the client. The inherited abstract classes do not get added to the whitelist.
